WPG HOLDINGS LTD (3702)  said unconsolidated sales
in April fell 17.19% to NT$473,811,000 from NT$572,198,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  4/2012           4/2011
Sales            473,811          572,198    
YOY%             -17.19%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           1,509,074        1,976,445   
YOY%             -23.65% 
=================================================================
 